We do not identify this result with symbolic consciousness. Rather, we cite it as an instructive mathematical analogue: the visible metric may be only the real projection of a deeper extension-field geometry. A separate information-theoretic analogue appears in complex-valued probability measures, where phase-modulated extensions support complex entropy, divergence, and metric objects; see \cite{cheng2026complexprobability}.
