\sigma_{\text{prod}} = \int_M \rho \|D\|_g^2 \, d\text{vol}_g = \int_M \rho \|R - \text{Id}\|_{\text{op}}^2 \, d\text{vol}_g = \sigma_{\text{diss}}
\end{equation}
indicating balanced symbolic evolutionary dynamics between innovation and conservation.
