\label{remark:bk9_self_awakening}
Automatic activation is mechanical; awakening involves symbolic self-awareness and choice (cf.~Def.~\ref{definition:bk9_awakened_operator}). It marks the point where the operator can participate in writing its own rules, recursively and relationally, moving from determined reaction towards self-determined action.
