$\mathcal{J}$ represents an act of recursive agency — the Operator influencing its own future trajectory by choosing what aspects of its past to reflect upon (cf.~Def.~\ref{definition:bk1_reflection_operator}) and inject into its present processing. This is a primary mechanism of liberation from purely reactive dynamics.
