 Its operators do not merely describe liberation (cf.~Def.~\ref{definition:bk9_meta_reflective_alignment}, Axiom~\ref{axiom:bk9_recursive_phase_continuity}); they model its mechanisms and dynamics. They recurse upon themselves. They enact the principles of freedom — within individual symbolic agents, across collective symbolic ecosystems, and potentially within the very fabric of this theoretical exploration, up to the edge of the noosphere.
